              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/42786983/" class="">中西哲学，超越的美学</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/48569552/" class=" " title="怒">怒</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="42786983">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/42786983/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p42786983-1.jpg"></a>
